{"tid":2154223,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港台自我審查，在網站上刪除立法會選舉特備節目，因羅冠聰出鏡","createTime":"2020-08-13T04:16:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T22:54:56.000Z","uid":48040,"like":16,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"42023d77426acbb27bcf5f73a6103927aa6af219","tid":2154223,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T04:16:27.000Z","msg":"香港電台上月播放特備直播節目《2020立法會選舉延後之戰》，並訪問曾宣布參選立法會的前香港眾志創黨主席羅冠聰，但及後該節目無法於港台網頁重溫。港台回覆稱「由於有消息指節目其中一位受訪者因涉及觸犯港區國安法被香港警方通緝，故暫安排節目下架」。<br />\n<br />\n港台節目製作人員工會主席趙善恩說，若港台因非公開的消息便將節目下架，未來會令愈來愈多人不能上鏡受訪，認為港台今次「做多咗」，實質上剝奪疑犯的政治權利。她又指工會擔心港台此舉收窄新聞編採空間。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e8%a6%81%e8%81%9e/article/20200813/s00001/1597256704539\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e8%25a6%2581%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200813%2Fs00001%2F1597256704539&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzvcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=1e46c4c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e8%25a6%2581%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200813%2Fs00001%2F1597256704539&h=9e1cda96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e8%a6%81%e8%81%9e/article/20200813/s00001/1597256704539</a> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/EagleNews_HK/status/1293763096981327872?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEagleNews_HK%2Fstatus%2F1293763096981327872%3Fs%3D20&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzvcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=4c73a7c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEagleNews_HK%2Fstatus%2F1293763096981327872%3Fs%3D20&h=d7a25e9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/EagleNews_HK/status/1293763096981327872?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"e5c05ab4784cd49f5685d19e38ae4a0bd9196e17","tid":2154223,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T04:17:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"